<exercise id="fs-id1163713353953">
<problem id="fs-id1163713487418">
<para id="fs-id1163713487420">A <m:math><m:mi>γ</m:mi></m:math>-ray photon has a momentum of <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8.00</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>−21</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mtext>kg</m:mtext><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mtext>m/s</m:mtext><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Find its wavelength and energy.</para>
